Package cmc.entity.dbmapping

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DoubleSchoolAttributeMetadata
    An implementation of SchoolAttributeMetadata for representing double fields in the School class.
    IntegerSchoolAttributeMetadata
    An implementation of SchoolAttributeMetadata for representing integer fields in the School class.
    SchoolAttributeMetadata
    SchoolAttributeMetadata holds relevant information for a School attribute.
    SchoolDatabaseMapping
    SchoolDatabaseMapping allows for easy conversion between database outputs and School objects, as well as iterable metadata of all School fields, which allows for easy programmatic manipulation of all school attributes.
    StringArraySchoolAttributeMetadata
    An implementation of SchoolAttributeMetadata for representing String array fields in the School class.
    StringSchoolAttributeMetadata
    An implementation of SchoolAttributeMetadata for representing String fields in the School class.
